{# twig template #}
{% extends 'base.html.twig' %}

{% block page_content %}

    {% embed 'layouts/right-sidebar.html.twig' %}

        {% block layout_page_title %}
            {{ 'Do you have clogged or dirty gutters?' }}
        {% endblock %}

        {% block layout_main_content %}
            <div class="col-12">

                <h2>Hire Your Local Gutter Cleaning Experts</h2>

                <p>Trust your home's care to the best gutter cleaner in the business. We provide top-quality gutter cleaning services in Byron, Warner Robins, Fort Valley, Macon, and Perry.</p>

                <div class="mb-3">
                    {% include 'components/image-carousel.html.twig' %}
                </div>

                <p>The difference starts with how we clean gutters. We don't use ladders, like you might think. We don't want to risk damaging your home, or falling from your roof.</p>

                <p>We use a high-powered vacuum system to 'suck' the gobs of dirt and leaves out of your gutters. It's state-of-the-art, and is powerful enough to pull root systems out of your gutters. Yes, we've seen trees growing in gutters!</p>

                <p>We can even record our work, using a wireless HD camera. You can <a class="text-link font-weight-bold" href="" data-toggle="modal" data-target="#vacuum-vid-modal">see the results</a> first-hand!
                </p>

                {# Call Now #}
                <div class="jumbotron jumbotron-fluid bg-white">
                    <div class="container">
                        <p class="lead">Ready To Get Your Gutters Cleaned?<span class="mr-2 ml-2"></span><a class="btn btn-danger btn-md" href="#" role="button">Call Now</a></p>
                    </div>
                </div>

                {# Checklist #}
                <h2>How Does It Work?</h2>
                <ul class="list-unstyled">
                    <li class="mb-3">
                        <p class="display-6 d-inline text-primary">
                            <i class="fa fa-check text-danger"></i>
                            &emsp;Schedule Your Free Quote
                        </p>
                        <p class="mt-2 ml-5">Fill out the short form on this page or call us at <i class="fas fa-phone text-danger"></i>&nbsp;<a class="text-link" href="tel:1-{{ company_phone }}">{{ company_phone | replace({'(': '', ') ': '-'}) }}</a>.</p>
                        <p class="ml-5">If you use our online form, we'll call you to schedule your free quote.</p>
                    </li>
                    <li class="mb-3">
                        <p class="display-6 d-inline text-primary">
                            <i class="fa fa-check text-danger"></i>
                            &emsp;A Pro Will Come to Your Home
                        </p>
                        <p class="mt-2 ml-5">Our gutter pro will come to your home to perform an inspection of your home's gutters, and provide you with a free custom quote. You just need to tell him when to start!</p>
                    </li>
                    <li class="mb-5">
                        <p class="display-6 d-inline text-primary">
                            <i class="fa fa-check text-danger"></i>
                            &emsp;Pay Online or In-Person
                        </p>
                        <p class="mt-2 ml-5">We can accept payments online or right at your front door. We accept all major credit cards, cash, and personal checks.</p>
                        <p class="ml-5">We can also email your invoice containing a link you can use to pay online.</p>
                    </li>
                </ul>

            </div>

        {% endblock %}

        {% block layout_sbr %}
            {% include 'components/forms/quote-request.html.twig' %}
            <div class="w-100 mb-3"></div>
            {% include 'components/testimonials.html.twig' %}
        {% endblock %}

    {% endembed %}

    {% include 'components/modals/vacuum-video.html.twig' %}

{% endblock %}